title: Off street parking requirement for various Planning Authorities / Areas shall be worked out by applying multiplying factor given in Table No
clause_text: Off street parking requirement for various Planning Authorities / Areas shall be worked out by applying multiplying factor given in Table No.8-C below. This multiplying factor shall be applied to the total quantum of parking spaces worked out as per Table No.8-B above.
